  triage:description "Two related issues: (1) The Sub-Task 4 doc-review deliverable (a document or inline annotation) required by sprint-A6.md is absent from the codebase. (2) crates/sc-lint-boundary/src/lib.rs lines 653-658 load the boundary inventory but discard the result — the loaded data is not used in the subsequent logic, making the load a no-op. Fix: (a) create the required Sub-Task 4 doc deliverable per sprint-A6.md spec, (b) fix lib.rs:653-658 to use the loaded inventory result instead of discarding it." ;
